## 🗄️ MASTER DATABASE ARCHITECTURE

### One Supabase Instance — Both Projects Read/Write It

```
Supabase (single project)
├── CRM Tables (staff, students, leads, tasks, events…)
├── Website CMS Tables (news_posts, events, website_courses…)
├── Shared Tables (offices, users, notifications, app_settings)
└── Auth (single auth system, role-based access)
```

**CRM Project** (`gtgroupcrmproject`) — Admin interface:
- CRUD on ALL tables
- Manages website content (CMS module)
- Manages staff, leads, HR, finance

**Web Project** (`gtgroupwebproject`) — Public face:
- READ-ONLY from website CMS tables
- Realtime subscriptions for live updates
- No auth required for public pages

### Environment Variables (Both Projects)
```env
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=<same value>
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=<same value>
```

