## ✨ TRANSPARENT GLASS UI DESIGN SPEC

### Glassmorphism Token Standard (v2.0)
```css
/* Premium Glass Card */
background: linear-gradient(135deg,
  rgba(239,183,72,0.06) 0%,
  rgba(255,255,255,0.04) 100%);
backdrop-filter: blur(24px) saturate(180%);
border: 1px solid rgba(239,183,72,0.15);
box-shadow:
  0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.4),
  inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
```

### Dark Mode (Default)
- Background: `#0C0E10` (deeper than before — near-black)
- Surface 1: `#121618` with glass overlay
- Surface 2: `#181A19` (brand dark)
- Sidebar: Frosted glass on brand dark

### Light Mode
- Background: `#F5F0E8` (warm off-white matching gold brand)
- Surface 1: `rgba(255,255,255,0.75)` glass
- Sidebar: `rgba(255,255,255,0.85)` glass

### Gold Glow Effects
```css
/* Active nav item glow */
box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(239,183,72,0.2), inset 0 0 20px rgba(239,183,72,0.05);

/* Button hover */
box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(239,183,72,0.4);
```

